text: The Nacionalista Party is the oldest political party in both the Philippines and Southeast Asia in general. It also ruled Philippines throughout the majority of the 20th century, from 1935–1946, 1953–1961 and 1965–1972. CalamBALIK or (former One Calamba), is a alliance party part of Nacionalista. == Team CalamBALIK == Category:Political parties in the Philippines
title: Nacionalista Party
